OL,3,CIslanders sign petition to call for
OL,4,Cimmediate repairs to Alderney runway
OL,6,FHundreds of islanders have signed a
OL,7,Fpetition calling for immediate repairs
OL,8,Fto Alderney's runway.
OL,10,FAround 540 islanders have signed the
OL,11,Fpetition that says resurfacing work is
OL,12,Fneeded to ensure the runway's
OL,13,Fcontinued operations.
OL,15,FThe petition states: "If this work
OL,16,Fdoes not start in Quarter 1 of 2025,
OL,17,Fthere is a serious risk to the entire
OL,18,Fisland's economy and a risk to life.
