OL,6,F"Our island does not have the luxury
OL,7,Fof a regular passenger boat service in
OL,8,Fthe winter due to our poor weather -
OL,9,Fso the airport is our only way to
OL,10,Faccess critical healthcare services."
OL,12,FThe States of Guernsey were
OL,13,Fprogressing with plans to extend the
OL,14,Flanding strip and build a new terminal.
OL,16,FPlans to spend #12.2 million to
OL,17,Fimprove the runway and airport
OL,18,Fballooned from #12.2 million in 2019
OL,19,Fto #24 million in 2022.
