OL,6,FGuernsey's Policy and Resources
OL,7,FCommittee then scrapped plans the
OL,8,Fsummer after costs rose again to #37
OL,9,Fmillion.
OL,11,FBut those who live in Alderney say
OL,12,Fplans need to be urgently prioritised,
OL,13,Fwith concerns that a recent visit from
OL,14,Fthe Civil Aviation Authority may force
OL,15,Fthe closure of the runway.
OL,17,FThis would leave 2,100 residents
OL,18,Fdependent on a seasonal ferry service,
OL,19,Fand potentially helicopters for
OL,20,Fmedivacs.
