OL,3,CIslanders sign petition to call for
OL,4,Cimmediate repairs to Alderney runway
OL,6,FDeputy Mark Helyar explains: "There's
OL,7,Fnobody else coming over the horizon to
OL,8,Ffix it. If it has to be the case that
OL,9,Fan external party has to step in and
OL,10,Ffund this, then we are putting our
OL,11,Findependence at risk.
OL,13,F"(It's) not just our independence but
OL,14,Fthe independence of the whole of the
OL,15,FChannel Islands because all we will
OL,16,Fhave done is demonstrate that we
OL,17,Fcannot govern ourselves properly."
OL,19,FStates of Guernsey will have to pay
OL,20,Ffor any approved plans.
