OL,6,FChief Minister Lyndon Trott says:
OL,7,F"We'll do our best to find the
OL,8,Fappropriate decision.
OL,10,F"It's important to remember that we're
OL,11,Ftalking about an enormous amount of
OL,12,Fmoney speaking to the 2,000 or so
OL,13,Fresidents."
OL,15,FA downgraded version of the plans is
OL,16,Fexpected to be put before the States
OL,17,Fof Guernsey in February 2025.
